    "As the amount and type of information per patient increase, multi-modality AI systems are expected to emerge, leading to an amplification of the black-box nature of AI systems. 3.",
    "Curse of dimensionality.",
    "With increasingly sophisticated -omics technologies, the dimensionality of data increases rapidly, thereby surpassing the number of cases, which remains similar over time.",
    "This phenomenon is described as the \"curse of dimensionality\" 44.",
